{
  "id": "6a16ef8e7f8b5669f3038ddf",
  "title": "知の「実質」と「IFF機能」は独立軸である",
  "created": 1779888017,
  "updated": 1779888038,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "6a16ef8e7f8b5669f3038ddf",
      "text": "知の「実質」と「IFF機能」は独立軸である",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779888017,
      "updated": 1779888017
    },
    {
      "id": "6a16ef900000000000ed430d",
      "text": "[tokoroten.icon]のClaudeの会話ログから自動生成された記事",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779888017,
      "updated": 1779888017
    },
    {
      "id": "6a16ef910000000000ed430e",
      "text": "----",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779888017,
      "updated": 1779888017
    },
    {
      "id": "6a16efa20000000000ed4312",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779888035,
      "updated": 1779888038
    },
    {
      "id": "6a16efa20000000000ed4313",
      "text": "[教養とリベラルアーツのIFF性] と [陰謀論は教養から排除された側の代替 IFF として機能する]",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779888035,
      "updated": 1779888035
    },
    {
      "id": "6a16efa20000000000ed4314",
      "text": "の議論から抽出した、より一般化したフレームワーク。",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779888035,
      "updated": 1779888035
    },
    {
      "id": "6a16efa20000000000ed4315",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779888035,
      "updated": 1779888035
    },
    {
      "id": "6a16efa20000000000ed4316",
      "text": "[*** 中核命題]",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779888035,
      "updated": 1779888035
    },
    {
      "id": "6a16efa20000000000ed4317",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779888035,
      "updated": 1779888035
    },
    {
      "id": "6a16efa20000000000ed4318",
      "text": "我々は知識・文化・教養を「実質の有無」で評価しがちだが、",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779888035,
      "updated": 1779888035
    },
    {
      "id": "6a16efa20000000000ed4319",
      "text": "[* 実質があるかどうかと、IFF として残酷に機能するかどうかは別の軸]である。",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779888035,
      "updated": 1779888035
    },
    {
      "id": "6a16efa20000000000ed431a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779888035,
      "updated": 1779888035
    },
    {
      "id": "6a16efa20000000000ed431b",
      "text": "\t[* 実質軸]: その知が世界の構造を理解する助けになるか、検証可能か、有用か",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779888035,
      "updated": 1779888035
    },
    {
      "id": "6a16efa20000000000ed431c",
      "text": "\t[* IFF軸]: その知の共有が in-group / out-group の識別装置として機能するか",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779888035,
      "updated": 1779888035
    },
    {
      "id": "6a16efa20000000000ed431d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779888035,
      "updated": 1779888035
    },
    {
      "id": "6a16efa20000000000ed431e",
      "text": "この 2 軸は[* 独立]に評価される必要がある。",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779888035,
      "updated": 1779888035
    },
    {
      "id": "6a16efa20000000000ed431f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779888035,
      "updated": 1779888035
    },
    {
      "id": "6a16efa20000000000ed4320",
      "text": "[*** 4 象限マップ]",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779888035,
      "updated": 1779888035
    },
    {
      "id": "6a16efa20000000000ed4321",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779888035,
      "updated": 1779888035
    },
    {
      "id": "6a16efa20000000000ed4322",
      "text": "table:table18",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779888035,
      "updated": 1779888035
    },
    {
      "id": "6a16efa20000000000ed4323",
      "text": " \tIFF 機能 強\tIFF 機能 弱",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779888035,
      "updated": 1779888035
    },
    {
      "id": "6a16efa20000000000ed4324",
      "text": " [* 実質 強]\t教養・専門知 (古典・哲学)\t道路の渡り方・四則演算",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779888035,
      "updated": 1779888035
    },
    {
      "id": "6a16efa20000000000ed4325",
      "text": " [* 実質 弱]\t陰謀論・カルト用語\tTV のタレント名",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779888035,
      "updated": 1779888035
    },
    {
      "id": "6a16efa20000000000ed4326",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779888035,
      "updated": 1779888035
    },
    {
      "id": "6a16efa20000000000ed4327",
      "text": "→ 「実質あり × IFF 強」と「実質なし × IFF 強」は、",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779888035,
      "updated": 1779888035
    },
    {
      "id": "6a16efa20000000000ed4328",
      "text": "[* IFF 機能としては鏡像]として作動する。",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779888035,
      "updated": 1779888035
    },
    {
      "id": "6a16efa20000000000ed4329",
      "text": "これが [陰謀論は教養から排除された側の代替 IFF として機能する] の鋭さの源泉。",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779888035,
      "updated": 1779888035
    },
    {
      "id": "6a16efa20000000000ed432a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779888035,
      "updated": 1779888035
    },
    {
      "id": "6a16efa20000000000ed432b",
      "text": "[*** エリート側の典型的反論と、その誤りの構造]",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779888035,
      "updated": 1779888035
    },
    {
      "id": "6a16efa20000000000ed432c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779888035,
      "updated": 1779888035
    },
    {
      "id": "6a16efa20000000000ed432d",
      "text": "教養を持つ側がしばしばする反論:",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779888035,
      "updated": 1779888035
    },
    {
      "id": "6a16efa20000000000ed432e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779888035,
      "updated": 1779888035
    },
    {
      "id": "6a16efa20000000000ed432f",
      "text": "> 「いやウチには (陰謀論と違って) 実質がある」",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779888035,
      "updated": 1779888035
    },
    {
      "id": "6a16efa20000000000ed4330",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779888035,
      "updated": 1779888035
    },
    {
      "id": "6a16efa20000000000ed4331",
      "text": "この反論は[* 実質軸では正しい]が、[* IFF 軸で起きていることを否認している]。",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779888035,
      "updated": 1779888035
    },
    {
      "id": "6a16efa20000000000ed4332",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779888035,
      "updated": 1779888035
    },
    {
      "id": "6a16efa20000000000ed4333",
      "text": "\tFC レーダー照射する側は「自分は照射した自覚がない」のが普通",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779888035,
      "updated": 1779888035
    },
    {
      "id": "6a16efa20000000000ed4334",
      "text": "\t同じく実質を持つ知の保持者は「自分が IFF として機能している自覚がない」",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779888035,
      "updated": 1779888035
    },
    {
      "id": "6a16efa20000000000ed4335",
      "text": "\t→ [* 実質の存在は IFF 機能を打ち消さない]",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779888035,
      "updated": 1779888035
    },
    {
      "id": "6a16efa20000000000ed4336",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779888035,
      "updated": 1779888035
    },
    {
      "id": "6a16efa20000000000ed4337",
      "text": "[*** マンガ『ようこそ！FACT へ』が突きつけるもの]",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779888035,
      "updated": 1779888035
    },
    {
      "id": "6a16efa20000000000ed4338",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779888035,
      "updated": 1779888035
    },
    {
      "id": "6a16efa20000000000ed4339",
      "text": "[陰謀論は教養から排除された側の代替 IFF として機能する] で扱ったが、",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779888035,
      "updated": 1779888035
    },
    {
      "id": "6a16efa20000000000ed433a",
      "text": "本作の核心は [* 2 軸の独立性を視覚化したこと]にある:",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779888035,
      "updated": 1779888035
    },
    {
      "id": "6a16efa20000000000ed433b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779888035,
      "updated": 1779888035
    },
    {
      "id": "6a16efa20000000000ed433c",
      "text": "\t渡辺は「実質ある教養」の IFF から排除された人物",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779888035,
      "updated": 1779888035
    },
    {
      "id": "6a16efa20000000000ed433d",
      "text": "\t陰謀論集団は「実質なき知」を IFF として提供する",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779888035,
      "updated": 1779888035
    },
    {
      "id": "6a16efa20000000000ed433e",
      "text": "\t機能的にはどちらも IFF として人を篩い落とす",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779888035,
      "updated": 1779888035
    },
    {
      "id": "6a16efa20000000000ed433f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779888035,
      "updated": 1779888035
    },
    {
      "id": "6a16efa20000000000ed4340",
      "text": "実質の有無で「健全 vs 不健全」を分けたい欲求は強いが、",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779888035,
      "updated": 1779888035
    },
    {
      "id": "6a16efa20000000000ed4341",
      "text": "[* 社会的に人を排除する力としては両者は同じ強度を持ちうる]。",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779888035,
      "updated": 1779888035
    },
    {
      "id": "6a16efa20000000000ed4342",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779888035,
      "updated": 1779888035
    },
    {
      "id": "6a16efa20000000000ed4343",
      "text": "[*** 設計含意 ([デジタル民主主義書] 文脈)]",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779888035,
      "updated": 1779888035
    },
    {
      "id": "6a16efa20000000000ed4344",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779888035,
      "updated": 1779888035
    },
    {
      "id": "6a16efa20000000000ed4345",
      "text": "\t専門書を書くとき、用語の「実質」(精度・効率) と「IFF 機能」(排除力) を[* 別々に評価する]",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779888035,
      "updated": 1779888035
    },
    {
      "id": "6a16efa20000000000ed4346",
      "text": "\t「これは実質があるから使っていい」は IFF 機能を見落とすための言い訳になりうる",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779888035,
      "updated": 1779888035
    },
    {
      "id": "6a16efa20000000000ed4347",
      "text": "\t用語選択は [* 2 軸両方の bookkeeping] が必要",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779888035,
      "updated": 1779888035
    },
    {
      "id": "6a16efa20000000000ed4348",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779888035,
      "updated": 1779888035
    },
    {
      "id": "6a16efa20000000000ed4349",
      "text": "[*** 設計含意 (フリーランス・コンサル文脈)]",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779888035,
      "updated": 1779888035
    },
    {
      "id": "6a16efa20000000000ed434a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779888035,
      "updated": 1779888035
    },
    {
      "id": "6a16efa20000000000ed434b",
      "text": "\tクライアントとの会話で[* 実質的に正確な用語]を使っても、",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779888035,
      "updated": 1779888035
    },
    {
      "id": "6a16efa20000000000ed434c",
      "text": "  IFF として機能して敵対視されるリスクは別途存在する",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779888035,
      "updated": 1779888035
    },
    {
      "id": "6a16efa20000000000ed434d",
      "text": "\t「正確だから問題ない」ではなく、「[* この場では IFF 軸でどう作動するか]」を考える",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779888035,
      "updated": 1779888035
    },
    {
      "id": "6a16efa20000000000ed434e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779888035,
      "updated": 1779888035
    },
    {
      "id": "6a16ef910000000000ed430f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779888017,
      "updated": 1779888017
    },
    {
      "id": "6a16ef910000000000ed4310",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "586cfba1be83a60011cafbcd",
      "created": 1779888018,
      "updated": 1779888018
    }
  ]
}